position.marginalia_text:
Multi hodiè Academici, volu[n]t esse Luciani Rhetores: Turnebi
artifices: Aula[e] philosophi: Agrippa[e] scientiarum professores:
pra[e]sertim maximè fallacium, vtilium, nobilium;

marginalia.translation:
More present and more vivid;
more clever and more loving;
everyone to the highest degree.
